{"tid":1986782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"願眾人幫幫手做份問卷","createTime":"2020-04-24T05:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T12:59:07.000Z","uid":354510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"587e3dd691f6c95763b0c155de870e0b045a54fa","tid":1986782,"uid":354510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"您好! 我是理工大學應用社會科學教授呂青湖的助理，現在進行一項有關抗爭與移民的研究。目的是理解香港人如何應對政治動盪。當中會問及有關您的政治立場、對最近發生「反送中」運動的想法、以及移民海外的可能性。不論您的立場是支持、反對、不關心、或不了解抗爭運動，都希望您能填寫這份問卷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此問卷大約需時15-20分鐘。受訪者年齡必須是18至65歲，香港永久居民，並且現居在香港。我們不會問及你個人或其他人參與抗爭的內容細節。此研究無需要您的個人資料(請不要留下名字, 身份証號碼等)。所有收集的資料只作研究用途。<br />\n<br />\n問卷限額為1000人。完成問卷後會得到$50百佳現金券。如果您同意參與, 請入：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_1TXv4LKHLSPBosR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_1TXv4LKHLSPBosR&d=nQ6Et69whbbCAj0%2Fbhy3hQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=8ea76f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_1TXv4LKHLSPBosR</a>"},{"pid":"eb37fb495c9c3f458c9c4029b2ba0b485ef6d896","tid":1986782,"uid":45687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"填咗<br />\n幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4712ad5ea541e7809a6a13532904b1d69fd9120d","tid":1986782,"uid":99299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ef6bfd82fb85dc37f64f86d6077e49152460fd4e","tid":1986782,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"push"}]}